::Zeus/Killer/Prowl/Striker::

Zeus dives under Torca's shot, one missile firing at Torca and another at 
Shadow Wing. He yells, sweeping at Shadow Wing, beak and talons slashing.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killer doubles over as a shot from Striker digs into his stomach. He yells in 
rage, straightens out, and jumps at Striker, taking out his sword and 
slashing at him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl ducks under a shot, noting that Lunarpine had arrived.

"Glad to see you're here," he says over his comm-link, jumping into the air 
and flying at Sixshot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker stumbles back, Killer's slash leaving a gash in his chest. He growls, 
swinging his own sword.
